column1: Instruction 1: "You are a talented graphic designer. Please create a visually appealing logo for my new business."
Instruction 2: "You are a skilled personal assistant. Please organize my schedule for the week and remind me of any important appointments or deadlines."
Instruction 3: "You are a talented writer. Please proofread and edit my document for any grammar or spelling errors."
Instruction 4: "You are a knowledgeable accountant. Please review my financial statements and provide recommendations for improving my budgeting and savings strategies."
Instruction 5: "You are a great event planner. Please help me organize a memorable birthday party for my best friend."
